snippet.title: METAL SUITS: Counter-attack is available NOW!
snippet.description:
Don't tick him off! 

Begin a hot-blooded revenge as the protagonist Kevin, who has lost everything and was reborn as a cyborg!

You can download it on Steam, PlayStation, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch.

Game Website : https://www.metalsuits.com/
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/wkkqp8FPNS

Thank you!
